# 📘 AI Literacy Study Guide

This repository is a **learning companion** for understanding **Artificial Intelligence (AI)**, **Machine Learning (ML)**, **Deep Learning (DL)**, **Transformers**, and **GPTs**.  

The guide is structured so you can:  
✅ Learn **core terms and concepts** quickly  
✅ Explore **lesson-by-lesson details** with explanations  
✅ See **connections across lessons**  
✅ Use **study drills** to reinforce knowledge  

